Content: Isolation is over, you're released from the cell floor.
The teacher is surprised to see you up but releases you.
The teacher is amazed to see you out but releases you.
The teacher grins to see you in the pillory but releases you.
The teacher grins to see you on the cross but releases you.
Hoping you've learned your lesson, you're released early.
You take what's left and escape from isolation with a grin.
You pick up your bag and make sure everything is still there.
You clean the dust on your clothes and head out for lunch.
